data.title: About: Alyce Cleese
data.meta_description: Alyce Faye Eichelberger Cleese (née McBride; born October 28, 1944) is an American psychotherapist, author and talk radio host. She was married to golfer Dave Eichelberger and later to actor-comedian John Cleese.
data.text:
dbo:abstract

Alyce Faye Eichelberger Cleese (née McBride; born October 28, 1944) is an American psychotherapist, author and talk radio host. She was married to golfer Dave Eichelberger and later to actor-comedian John Cleese. (en)
